data.description: Open House Canceled.  A delightful & inviting home. Next to golf club greenway w/gated direct access and super privacy. Newer 50-yr. roof w/gutters; newer electrical panel and high-efficiency gas furnace & AC. Updated kitchen w/tons of cabinets inc granite/tile countertops. High-end Mascotte security door and some custom blinds. A gardener’s delight w/several raised garden beds, several fruit trees on large lot. Backyard & covered deck perfect for entertaining or quiet relaxation. 4th-bed has bath.
